lead_paragraph: The defending champion Nadia Petrova was upset by Kateryna Bondarenko, 7-6 (4), 3-6, 6-4, in the first round of the Open Gaz de France in France. Amélie Mauresmo, a two-time winner, cruised past the American qualifier Julie Ditty, 6-1, 6-2.
